caption.p: Post inflammatory response. The levels of inflammatory cytokines; ( A, B) IL-6, and ( C, D) IFN-γ were evaluated in the lung samples after the virus challenges. Lung samples were prepared on day 4 post-challenge and the cytokines were estimated by ELISA. Results are represented as the mean ± SD (n = 5). (*P < 0.05, **P < 0.01).
